FANCY PANTS ADVENTURES - PRIVACY POLICY
DATA COLLECTION
In short:
We do not collect any personal information in or through the Fancy Pants Adventure game or app.
Our Apps only request access to provide core functionality (save files, access files).
We do not store or share any of this data with anyone.
In some of our Apps we use third party networks to display Ads and monetize. These ad networks might collect data to provide you with personalized ads.
Our Third Party Ad Networks are: Google Ads, Facebook, Applovin, Unity and InMobi.
By default we don't allow these networks to display personalized Ads, but in some occasions you might be prompted when launching our Apps for your permission
